## Mission: Support small business owners

## The problem: It is expensive and complicated to start and sustain a small business.

## ##
## Requirements ##
# It should be easier to set up a small business
# Taxes should be easier to understand and file
# Insurance costs should be less
# Small businesses are also consumers. 
# Consumer protection is critical for owners, employees, and customers.
## ##

### Policy Recommendations: ###
# Tax code should be less complicated (see also Tax Code Policy)
# Less taxes due (see also Tax Code Policy)
# Individual and group insurance for small business owners should be cheaper and more options. (See also healthcare)
    # They should be able to opt in themselves and employees to programs like Medicaid. 
